articles.title: Siegemund upsets Zheng; Sabalenka holds on at Australian Open - WTA Tennis
articles.description: Defending champion Aryna Sabalenka held on for a tough second-round win at the Australian Open on Wednesday, but last year's finalist Zheng Qinwen became the first Top 10 seed to fall this week.
articles.content: Last year's Australian Open finalists Aryna Sabalenka and Zheng Qinwen both faced dramatic challenges in their second-round matches at the Australian Open on Wednesday. Sabalenka held on for the win,… [+4448 chars]
